Define AlyvixProbeAlias SERVERHOSTNAME
Define AlyvixProbeFQDN  serverfqdn_all_lowercase

SSLProxyEngine on
SSLProxyVerify none
SSLProxyCheckPeerCN off
SSLProxyCheckPeerName off
SSLProxyCheckPeerExpire off
ProxyPass /alyvix/${AlyvixProbeAlias}/ https://${AlyvixProbeFQDN}/
ProxyPassReverse /alyvix/${AlyvixProbeAlias}/ https://${AlyvixProbeFQDN}/
